Author: Sarah St Cyr
Content: Thank you Baby! We were Blessed this week to obtain the ingredients to do this! G-Ranata needs your prayers and more healing to. Shes feeling the heavy weights of her struggles too and we all need healp with that together as well as you and others we have yet to know too who will need the right to heal the right to be prayed for and the right to healing food choice in all struggling places because all of us who struggle with chronic illness or in the way there or will be is going to need those freedoms and an environment and community that allows it or no one will be allowed to continue to heal! No one Can do Medical Medium without those Basics! I know I dont want everyones struggles through such hard times to heal to be in vain nor it be denied the rights of these to the support for others to become vain in this way either. Pain has a way of making our decisions foggy and cloudy and limits our abilities when individuals have to carry so much when it wasnt designed to be that way by GOD. But then something happened and the first person in history who was sensitive started to feel under or overstimulized and told another and they didnt understand because they either didnt know what that felt like or because they too were starting to feel their senses and sensitivities highten in ways they didnt quite no how to cope with because it was new to humanity to experience so no one could teach them how save for turning their Pain and sensitivity to GOD to give them strength and More ComPassionate Spirit (SOC) to do so so they can healp eachother grow their sensitivity powers in a healthy way instead of destroying their ComPassionate sensibilities and abilities!
